						<summary>

						<p>Aparādhakshamēśvara Temple-Central Shrine, north base.</p>						

						<p><hi rend="bold">Tribhuvanachakravartti Kō[nērinma]koṇḍāṉ Year 4, 212 day</hi></p>						

						<p>This records a royal gift of 20 <hi rend="italic">vēli</hi> of land as <hi rend="italic">dēvadāna-iṟai-ili,</hi> to contribute 20 <hi rend="italic">kalam</hi> per <hi rend="italic">vēli</hi> for the conduct of necessary services to God Tirukku-[raṅgāḍutuṟai]-uḍaiya-Mahādēvar in [Iṟai]yān-puñchey in Ugaḷūrkūṟṟam alias Teṉūr-v[āḍakai] in Muḍikoṇḍa-chōḷa-vaḷanāḍu. The record was authenticated by Vallavarājaṉ.</p>						

						</summary>
